CustomField.description: GeoResults modeled ranking score (0-100) indicating the likelihood of a telecommunications decision maker being at this business location. A high score indicates that the decision maker is very likely on site and a low score indicates a very small likelihood that the decision maker is at this business location.

CustomField.label: Autonomous Score
